msgctxt "56_Kiryu"
msgid "So... engagement rings, huh?"
msgstr "Con que... anillos de compromiso, eh?"

msgctxt "68_Chigusa"
msgid "Let's put them on. They're a pair, after all."
msgstr "Pongámonoslos. Al fin y al cabo, van a juego."

msgctxt "80_Kiryu"
msgid "As long as you're sure."
msgstr "Si te parece bien."

msgctxt "104_Kiryu"
msgid "It's... too small for my finger."
msgstr "Es... muy pequeño para mi dedo."

msgctxt "116_Chigusa"
msgid "*sob*"
msgstr "*solloza*"

msgctxt "128_Kiryu"
msgid "Hey, what's wrong?"
msgstr "Oye, ¿pasa algo?"

msgctxt "140_Chigusa"
msgid "I give up..."
msgstr "Me rindo..."

msgctxt "152_Chigusa"
msgid "Yusaku's... He's gone. *sob*"
msgstr "Yusaku... ya no está. *sollozo*"

msgctxt "164_Kiryu"
msgid "Chigusa..."
msgstr "Chigusa..."

msgctxt "176_Chigusa"
msgid "I've known all this time! I just..."
msgstr "¡Lo he sabido todo este tiempo! Solo que..."

msgctxt "188_Chigusa"
msgid "Forget it. Just let me be alone."
msgstr "Olvídalo. Déjame estar sola."

msgctxt "200_Kiryu"
msgid "I don't think that's gonna help. We should go somewhere we\\r\n"\n"can sit and take a breather."
msgstr "No creo que eso sea de ayuda. Deberíamos ir a algun lugar\\r\n"\n"donde podamos sentarnos y tomar un respiro."

msgctxt "212_Chigusa"
msgid "...Fine. Let's go back to Bantam, then. Yusaku and I used to\\r\n"\n"go there together all the time."
msgstr "...Bueno. Volvamos a Bantam. Yusaku y yo solíamos\\r\n"\n"ir ahí juntos todo el tiempo."

msgctxt "224_Kiryu"
msgid "Got it. Let's go."
msgstr "De acuerdo. Vamos."

